{"tid":1334253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你唔帶口罩係連累緊身邊既人","createTime":"2019-07-20T04:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T04:47:15.000Z","uid":270154,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"02abc935d1bda3cbea39587a95c0830fa9657782","tid":1334253,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"你唔帶口罩係連累緊身邊既人<br />\n<br />\n聽日遊行預計人數都唔會太少，幾十萬人塞滿軒尼詩道，相信會引來唔少好奇心旺盛既人影相。如果你對鏡頭敏感，麻煩帶番個口罩。你唔帶，就會有好多行俠仗義之士因顧及你而同影相既人發起爭執。你害到既就唔止係自己。如果你好唔想上鏡，請自己避鏡頭，或打扮成被人影到都唔介意既模樣。<br />\n最後，我係度警告，男士唔好再觸碰女性，男女授受不親。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/九龍遊行-拍照被當便衣警-女子遭箍頸包圍-警拘三人涉非法禁錮非禮等/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%8B%8D%E7%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E7%95%B6%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6-%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%81%AD%E7%AE%8D%E9%A0%B8%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E9%8C%AE%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE%E7%AD%89%2F%23&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbtqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=26ade70d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%8B%8D%E7%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E7%95%B6%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6-%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%81%AD%E7%AE%8D%E9%A0%B8%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E9%8C%AE%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE%E7%AD%89%2F%23&h=6a8e306c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/九龍遊行-拍照被當便衣警-女子遭箍頸包圍-警拘三人涉非法禁錮非禮等/#</a>"},{"pid":"b08fd64997dfb72b8e85f3e4401a11bec1e4de89","tid":1334253,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b974bcc79fbb47d10fd294fc3e9448f63584e08","tid":1334253,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:41:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11871d5e2bde80bcb401eaa3630e7a5e8d421634","tid":13342